5, 255, 255);">市文明单位、</span><font face="arial, 宋体, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">南京市</span></font><span style="font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">教科研先进集体，江苏省篮球传统学校。</span></p>');
